name: Tezos Postcards #1 "Welcome to Nice"
description: Tezos Postcards are 1 of 1 Postcards. There will be 100 Tezos Postcards total. This postcard features my original video and animation work while on a trip to Nice, France with my wife in 2020. This gentleman was pretty relaxed and soaking in the rays. All music, video, and artwork were done by the NFT creator Clipdad. This is a 600 x 338 MP4 Music Video. The song is "Haw Eye" by Clipdad.
